      "title": "The President will resign on the 13th",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Speaker Mr. Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena states that President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa informed him that President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa will resign from his post on the 13th.",
        "The Speaker said in a statement to the media that the President mentioned that the power would be handed over peacefully."
